node.text:
The F-117 Nighthawk was the very first true stealth fighter. But it came with one significant drawback: it could barely fly. Here’s why. 🧐

Find out more information in the link in bio 🚀
#engineering

node.title: Why the F-117 Nighthawk is elusive and legendary
